content.value: Add a Flowknit Ultra-Soft Performance Tee for only $14.90 $19.90 (25% off)
Also, add an Organic No-Show Sock 3-pack for only $8.90 $12.90

The perfect crewneck sweater made from 100% Australian merino wool. This merino wool sweater features a smooth and soft texture with a flattering silhouette. A high-quality, comfy piece made to be layered or worn solo. In other words, what every merino sweater should be.
Merino wool is 100% biodegradable, renewable, wrinkle resistant, UV resistant, and naturally breathable
Material: 100% Extra-fine Australian merino wool; 19.5 micron yarn quality
Produced in BSCI (Business Social Compliance Initiative) certified factories which aims to improve working conditions throughout the supply chain.
Origin: Fujian, China
Model is 6'1 wearing our merino wool sweater in a size Medium
Hand wash only.  Cold wash inside out. Lay flat to dry. Cool iron, or dry clean.
